<%# INTRODUCTION %>
  <div id="introduction" class="single__wrapper">
    <div class="single__content" style="margin-bottom: 0;">
      <a href="#introduction" class="guide__suggestion guide__suggestion__padding">
        <div class="guide__suggestion__number guide__suggestion__number--bottom">1.</div>
      </a>
      <h2 class="single__sub__header">Introduction</h2>
      <p>NeverFap Deluxe offers a wide range of effective Meditation solutions and options for those seeking additional help.</p>
      <p>The aim of our meditations is to teach you the fundamental basics of meditation, so you can have the ability to comfortably practice meditation on your own.</p>
      <h3>It's not within our intention to sell you a monthly meditation subscription like many existing options.</h3>
      <p>Not only is it a waste of money, however it largely defeats the purpose and aim of NeverFap Deluxe which is to teach you to become truly autonomous in every sense of the word.</p>
      <p>Instead we offer a range of inexpensive, one-time payment options which provide you with a range of different skills dependent upon what you aim to achieve and your skill level.</p>
      <p>Of course, we also offer a heap of <a class="link" href="/meditation-reading-list">FREE meditation articles</a> which provide invaluable tips and advice on how best to meditate.</p>
      <p>With that said, there's ultimately no substitution to using Guided Meditations when starting out, and certainly it made all the difference to helping me understand meditation when I was starting out.</p>
      <p>I simply want to provide you with a more effective and more affordable option than what I personally had to go through to reach the same knowledge.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <%= partial "links/twitter.html", assigns %>
<%# INTRODUCTION END %>


<%# FREE GUIDED MEDITATION SERIES %>
  <div id="free_guided_meditation_series" class="single__wrapper">
    <div class="single__content" style="margin-bottom: 0;">
      <a href="#introduction" class="guide__suggestion guide__suggestion__padding">
        <div class="guide__suggestion__number guide__suggestion__number--bottom">2.</div>
      </a>

      <h2 class="single__sub__header">Free Guided Meditation Series</h2>
      <p>Below are our series of free guided meditations for those looking for some assistance with their daily meditation practice.</p>
      <p>Unfortunately I don't have the time, money, nor resources to produce them frequently - although I try to create them when the time arises.</p>
      <p></p>
      <div class="podcast__item__container">
        <%= Enum.map(@page_collections.meditations, fn(meditation) -> %>
          <div class="podcast__item">
            <a href='<%= Routes.content_path(@conn, :meditation, meditation["slug"]) %>'><h1 style="margin-bottom: 0;"><%= meditation["title"] %></h1></a>
            <h3 style="margin-bottom: 1rem;"><%= raw meditation["content"] %></h3>
            <div class="podcast__item__bottom">
              <a class="link articles__link" href='<%= meditation["podcast_url"] %>'>episode link</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        <% end ) %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <%= partial "links/discord.html", assigns %>
<%# FREE GUIDED MEDITATION SERIES END %>


<%# FUNDAMENTAL SERIES %>
  <div id="fundamental_meditation_series" class="single__wrapper">
    <div class="single__content" style="margin-bottom: 0;">
      <a href="#fundamental_meditation_series" class="guide__suggestion guide__suggestion__padding">
        <div class="guide__suggestion__number guide__suggestion__number--bottom">3.</div>
      </a>
      <h2 class="single__sub__header">Fundamental Meditation Series</h2>
      <p>As a primary option we offer the <b>Fundamental Meditation Series</b> which is a series of 4 meditations which is designed to teach you the absolute core fundamental basics of meditation.</p>
      <p>It is a perfect starting point for those new to meditation, and with this core knowledge you should have the skills in order to meditate on your own.</p>
      <p>As a starting point for your meditation journey, I also wanted it to be cheap enough that anyone can afford it, because I believe basic mental health should be inexpensive.</p>
      <h3>It's available for $9 USD.</h3>
      <p>The price of a nice meal, and if you can't sacrifice a meal for the empowerment of your mental health, then I'm not quite sure how to help you.</p>
      <p>Of course, I've also written <a class="link" href='<%= Routes.content_path(@conn, :practice, "observe-your-senses") %>'>A Definitive Guide On How To Meditate Properly</a> if you're wanting to learn the basics of how to meditate, although it's not quite the same as being guided through it from a 3rd person perspective.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="line__top"></div>
  <div class="line__bottom"></div>

  <%= partial "banners/fdm_banner.html", assigns %>

