<%# FUNDAMENTAL SERIES END %>


<%# HOVERING MEDITATION %>
  <div id="hovering_meditation" class="single__wrapper">
    <div class="single__content" style="margin-bottom: 0;">
      <a href="#hovering_meditation" class="guide__suggestion guide__suggestion__padding">
        <div class="guide__suggestion__number guide__suggestion__number--bottom">4.</div>
      </a>
      <h2 class="single__sub__header">Hovering Meditation</h2>
      <p>One thing I've noticed is that a lot of people struggle to meditate via traditional means.</p>
      <p>In part due to poor mental health or "brain fog" which makes it incredibly difficult to engage with our minds in a meaningful way.</p>
      <p>That's why I created Hovering: A meditation technique which aims to bridge the gap between traditional meditation and simply not meditating at all.</p>
      <p>It has been designed to be easy to understand, simple to practice, as well as remain acessible to people of all ages.</p>
      <p>If you would like to learn more about Hovering I highly encourage you to visit the <a class="link" href="/hovering">NeverFap Deluxe Hovering</a> section which provides a basics overview of the practice.</p>

      <img style="width: 100%;" src="https://neverfapdeluxe.netlify.com/images/hovering_web.png"/>

      <p>Alternatively you can visit the <a class="link" href="https://tryhovering.com/">Hovering Website</a> which provides a much more comprehensive overview of Hovering.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="line__top"></div>
  <div class="line__bottom"></div>

  <%= partial "banners/hovering_banner.html", assigns %>

  <div class="line__top"></div>
  <div class="line__bottom"></div>
<%# HOVERING MEDITATION END %>


