<%# NEXT STEPS ARTICLES %>
  <div id="next_steps" class="single__wrapper">
    <div class="single__content" style="margin-bottom: 0;">
      <a href="#next_steps" class="guide__suggestion guide__suggestion__padding">
        <div class="guide__suggestion__number guide__suggestion__number--bottom">5.</div>
      </a>
      <h2 class="single__sub__header">Next Steps</h2>
      <p>The resources on this page should be more-than-enough for you to develop a solid meditation routine.</p>
      <p>In most cases, all it takes is 10 minutes of meditation each night before bed, and that should be enough for most people to be able to remain calm and maintain balance throughout the day.</p>
      <p>Of course, like all things, meditation is simply a tool to help you maintain balance in your daily life. If you're not eating healthily or respecting boundaries, then no amount of meditation will help you improve.</p>
      <p>Once you're comfortable with your meditation routine, I would highly recommend checking out of our <a href="/practices" class="link">NeverFap Deluxe Practices</a> in order to spend some time working on your awareness and mental health.</p>
      <p>They consist of a series of exercises, much like meditation, which are designed to teach you mental health best practice, as well as offer perspective throughout your day.</p>
      <p>There is also the <a href="/articles" class="link">NeverFap Deluxe Articles</a> section on the website which consists of a large range of in-depth articles explaining the porn addiction recovery process.</p>
      <p>Just remember that no matter what, as a human being you absolutely have the capacity to overcome your porn addiction.</p>
      <p>It's simply a matter of process and education, two things which NeverFap Deluxe offers whole-heartedly.</p>
      <p>Oh, and here's an emoji of a dog to keep you motivated.</p>
      <p>U・ᴥ・U</p>
    </div>
  </div>
<%# NEXT STEPS ARTICLES END %>


